This is an empty Angular2/Express/Node.js project.

Fork this repository when starting a new project.

1. Run 'apt-get install nodejs'
2. Run 'npm install' in the project root to install npm packages
3. Install tsc and typings will be useful to have installed globally. Do 'npm install -g tsc typings'
4. run 'typings install' in the client and server directories
5. Use 'tsc -p [ client | server ]' to build the client and server, respectively
6. Use 'npm start' to run the server
